<plot>Indian-born and brought up Vani is in love with U.K. born John. Vani's family does not approve of John, and he decides to get them to change their minds about him. In order to do this, he meets with Swamiji, a man with magical powers, and requests him to make him invisible. The Swami reluctantly agrees, but while chanting the magic words, something goes wrong, and John is transformed into a Tom-thumb like person. The Swami is unable to get John back to his original size, until he finds and brings him a ring. Thus John sets off on a trek that he may not be lift by himself, leave alone carry it and bring it to the Swami.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?338161</url></doc>
